<div id="review_603606225" class="review nosyndicate" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/603606225" />
    <a title="Wanda" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/9246169-wanda"><img alt="Wanda" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1528903039p2/9246169.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/603606225?book_show_action=true">Apr 30, 2013</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Wanda" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Wanda" href="/user/show/9246169-wanda">Wanda</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>



        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/9246169-wanda?shelf=serial-murderers">serial-murderers</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/9246169-wanda?shelf=mysteries-thrillers">mysteries-thrillers</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/9246169-wanda?shelf=read-in-2013">read-in-2013</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/9246169-wanda?shelf=female-authors">female-authors</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/9246169-wanda?shelf=time-travel">time-travel</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer603606225" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer3627732358965252735">Wow. Just wow.<br/><br/>I&apos;m amazed at the mixed reviews that this book has received. I loved it.<br/><br/>A time traveling serial killer. A girl who survived his attack. She tries to put her life back together and to put an end to his murdering ways.<br/><br/>I felt deliciously drunk on time, as the chapters changed POV and year, but all clearly marked by the title heading. During the last several chapters, my feet were making little running motions and I kept checking to see how many pages of tension were left. That&apos;s rare.</span>
  <span id="freeText3627732358965252735" style="display:none">Wow. Just wow.<br /><br />I'm amazed at the mixed reviews that this book has received. I loved it.<br /><br />A time traveling serial killer. A girl who survived his attack. She tries to put her life back together and to put an end to his murdering ways.<br /><br />I felt deliciously drunk on time, as the chapters changed POV and year, but all clearly marked by the title heading. During the last several chapters, my feet were making little running motions and I kept checking to see how many pages of tension were left. That's rare.<br /><br />What is also rare? The killer doesn't come off as sexy or overly intelligent or all that slick. In short, he is not glorified at all. And the women/girls are truly shining ones--shining with intelligence, potential and determination.<br /><br />I would recommend this novel highly.<br /></span>
  <a data-text-id="3627732358965252735" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
